Package retailStore

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    App
    This is Front end app, its an interactive console-based menu and it uses InventoryManager class to communicate with Back end
    Inventory
    This class creates many Tool classes and store them in a local variable .
    InventoryManager
    This class reads the item.txt and supplier.txt and creates a Inventory class and many Order classes Note: The way this class is set up, it receives a string of all tools that should be ordered then create new Order
    Order
    This class simply creates a string for all the tools ordered for the day.It is created in #generateOrder(java.util.ArrayList)
    Tool
    This class simply stores the info that each tool has, example name,id,price..etc
